short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds context menu items to open a frame (or iframe) in the current tab, a new tab, new window, or incognito window.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds context menu items to open a frame (or iframe) in the current tab, a new tab, new window, or incognito window. This extension will copy and use the frame URL to open the new tab or window.
